            bindings = <
        &none         &none         &none          &none      &none      &kp K_REDO    &kp K_PASTE     &kp K_COPY     &kp K_CUT     &kp K_UNDO
        &kp LEFT_WIN  &kp LEFT_ALT  &kp RA(LCTRL)  &kp LSHFT  &none      &kp CAPSLOCK  &kp LEFT_ARROW  &kp DOWN       &kp UP_ARROW  &kp RIGHT
